      "text": "……凄い食欲だな、怜\n俺より食べてないか？",
      "startTime": 18.0356463313,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルは体力勝負ですから\nあっすみません、追加オーダーいいですか？",
      "startTime": 22.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00",
      "startTime": 26.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "……なぁ怜。カウントダウンライブまであと数日だけど\n……そんなに食べて大丈夫か？",
      "startTime": 32.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_03_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに心配しないで下さい\n{user}さん、私はプロですよ？",
      "startTime": 37.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
